== About Me
	- I am currently a Ph.D. candidate at the [https://ece.uic.edu Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering], [http://www.uic.edu/ University of Illinois at Chicago]. I work at [https://waveopt-lab.uic.edu WaveOPT lab], UIC under supervision of [https://msol.people.uic.edu/ Prof. Mojtaba Soltanalian]  since 2016.
	- I received my B.Tech in Electronics and Communication Engineering from [http://www.wbut.ac.in/ West Bengal University of Technology], India in 2012.
	- Before joining UIC, I spent my time doing software designing, development, and maintenance as an IT specialist. I have almost one and half years of work experience in [https://www.cognizant.com/ Cognizant Technology Solutions] as a Java Developer during 2013-14.
	- Above everything, I am a part time artist and amateur photographer. My subject is mostly abstract, and black and white is my color. 

